title: Did Bobby’s Girlfriend Move In With Him? + Morgan2 Is Quarantined During ‘Celebrities Over 50’ Draft + Lunchbox On The Street: What Country Artist Would You Want To Babysit Your Kids?
itunes:title: Did Bobby’s Girlfriend Move In With Him? + Morgan2 Is Quarantined During ‘Celebrities Over 50’ Draft + Lunchbox On The Street: What Country Artist Would You Want To Babysit Your Kids?
description:
Bobby had listeners hitting him up on Instagram because of something he said to his girlfriend. They claim he declared his love for her! We draft our favorite celebrities over 50 years old, but Morgan2 is quarantined for going out to the bar this weekend..so she calls in her draft picks! Plus, Lunchbox hits the streets asking people “What country artist would you want to babysit your kids?”.
